_description: Gospel for the Sunday after the Nativity, in the Northern Homily Cycle

CULGg531.First Lines:
Þyse iewes made ilk a ȝereSeuen festes in þaire
                    manere…
CULGg531.Last Lines:
…ffor iewes fell fro all gudeWhen þai show crist on
                    þe rode

Dominica infra octavas nativitatis domini secundum lucam (f.
                    27)
